Sentencas: Oxygen isotope diffusion coefficients were determined for La1-xCaxCrO3-delta (x = 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) via bulk and via grain-boundary diffusion as functions of calcium content (x), temperatures from 1073 to 1273 K, and oxygen partial pressures from p(O-2) = 10(-9) to 10(4) Pa at T = 1273 K. Both bulk and grain-boundary diffusion coefficients increased with calcium content.
Titulo: Oxygen transport properties of La1-xCaxCrO3-δ as an interconnect material of a solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: For La0.8Ca0.2CrO3-delta, the activation energy is 160 and 167 kJ mol(-1) for bulk and grain-boundary diffusion, respectively.
Titulo: Oxygen transport properties of La1-xCaxCrO3-δ as an interconnect material of a solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The bulk-diffusion coefficient increased with decreasing oxygen partial pressure.
Titulo: Oxygen transport properties of La1-xCaxCrO3-δ as an interconnect material of a solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The oxygen vacancy diffusion coefficient was calculated as (1.7 +/- 0.5) X 10(-9) m(2) s(-1) at T = 1273 K, constant regardless of calcium content or oxygen-vacancy content.
Titulo: Oxygen transport properties of La1-xCaxCrO3-δ as an interconnect material of a solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The effect of surface change on the oxygen permeation through La1-xCaxCrO3-delta was quantitatively evaluated.
Titulo: Oxygen transport properties of La1-xCaxCrO3-δ as an interconnect material of a solid oxide fuel cell
